15:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda homiladorlik va tug'ish ta'tili 126 kalendar kun: tug'ishdan 70 kun oldin va 56 kun keyin. Asoratli tug'ish yoki ko'p homilada tug'ishdan keyingi qism 70 kungacha oshiriladi (jami 140 kun). 2026-yil 1-yanvardan homiladorlik va tug'ish nafaqasi bevosita DSSF (Davlat sug'urta ijtimoiy fondi) mablag'laridan to'lanadi. Nafaqa miqdori sug'urta stajiga bog'liq: 10-24 oy stajda — o'rtacha ish haqining 75%, 25-60 oy — 85%, 61 oy va undan ko'p — 100%. Nafaqa olish uchun kamida 10 oylik sug'urta staji talab qilinadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"2 yoshgacha bolaga qarashuv nafaqasi o'rtacha oylik ish haqining 50% ni tashkil etadi, lekin minimal ish haqining 50% (635 500 so'm) dan kam emas. 2 yilgacha qarashuv ta'tili ish joyini saqlash bilan, 3 yilgacha — saqlashsiz, lekin avvalgi lavozimga qaytish huquqi bilan beriladi. Ta'tilni nafaqat ona, balki ota, buvi, bobo yoki bolaga haqiqatda qarayotgan boshqa qarindosh ham olishi mumkin."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Bola tug'ilganda bir martalik nafaqa ish beruvchi mablag'laridan to'lanadi: birinchi bolaga — 2 "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" (824 000 so'm), ikkinchiga — 3 BHK (1 236 000 so'm), uchinchi va keyingilarga — 4 BHK (1 648 000 so'm). Qo'shimcha ravishda davlat ijtimoiy himoya tizimi orqali 2 yoshgacha bolali oilalarga oylik nafaqa to'laydi — miqdori oila daromadi va bolalar soniga bog'liq."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Dekret nafaqasi "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" va ijtimoiy soliqqa tortilmaydi. Hisoblash uchun o'rtacha ish haqi dekretga chiqqan oydan oldingi oxirgi 12 oy uchun aniqlanadi. Agar ayol 12 oydan kam ishlagan bo'lsa, haqiqiy davr olinadi. Bir nechta ish joyini qo'shib olib borsangiz, nafaqa har bir ish joyi bo'yicha alohida hisoblanadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Dekret nafaqasini hisoblash misoli (sug'urta staji 61 oydan ortiq — 100%): o'rtacha ish haqi 15 000 000 so'm/oy, o'rtacha kunlik ≈ 500 000 so'm. Homiladorlik va tug'ish nafaqasi = 500 000 × 126 = 63 000 000 so'm (soliqqa tortilmaydi). 25-60 oy stajda (85%) nafaqa 53 550 000 so'm, 10-24 oy stajda (75%) — 47 250 000 so'm bo'ladi. 2 yilgacha qarashuv nafaqasi = MROTning 60% = 762 600 so'm/oy (24 oy = 18 302 400 so'm). Bir martalik (1-bola) = 824 000 so'm. Butun davr uchun jami: ~244 mln so'm."}]]}]]}]]}],"$L1b","$L1c","$L1d"]}]
